This is a placeholder. In production, replace with actual 192x192 PNG icon.
For now, the app will work without it, but you should add proper icons before final deployment.

To generate icons quickly:
1. Use https://realfavicongenerator.net/
2. Upload a logo (green leaf or plant icon)
3. Download the generated icons
4. Replace this file with icon-192.png
5. Also add icon-512.png

Or use this simple SVG as icon for now - save as PNG:
<svg width="192" height="192" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
  <rect width="192" height="192" fill="#10b981"/>
  <text x="96" y="120" font-size="100" text-anchor="middle" fill="white">🌱</text>
</svg>